Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;あんたが好きらしいね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;俺は弾なんざいらねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;痛てて…
